http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/Kochi/Power-supply-to-be-regulated-in-Kochi-city/article14013878.ece

Power supply to following areas under different electrical sections will be disrupted on Friday: Vaduthala - stretch between Karshaka road and Pallikkavu Centre road, Chinmaya, up to Kattungal Temple on Chittoor road (8 a.m. to 6 p.m.); Vytilla - Thykoodam Church road, St. Antony’s road, L.M. Paily road, and NH Bypass road (10 a.m. to 2 p.m.); Tripunithura - Star Homes, Chathary, RCM, Kizhakkekotta, Police Station; Boys High School, municipal bus stand, hospital road, and Kannankulangara (9 a.m. to 4 p.m.); Thoppumpady – Mathuttyparambu and Statue (9 a.m. to 5 p.m.); College – between sewerage and Muthoot and areas near Mullassery Canal (10 p.m. and 5 a.m.); Thevara – areas near water tank and areas near Mattammal junction (9.30 a.m. to 4 p.m.); Eroor – Illikkalppady, Puthiya Road, Nayar Samajam and near Federal Bank (9 a.m. to 3 p.m.)